{"tid":365753,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"曬到古銅色 踢拖遊走緬甸南至北","createTime":"2017-08-19T13:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T08:50:44.000Z","uid":61690,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"201b85b983c9dfdaf1213d6a0eb4c7667c021c27","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:05:23.000Z","msg":"我打呢篇遊記主要俾個機會自己重新&rdquo;去多次&rdquo;緬甸<br />\n而我好興幸我認識到緬甸呢個國家<br />\n亦都推薦有興趣既巴絲去返轉<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多, 去一去圖先, 呢幾張係我覺得幾&rdquo;緬甸&rdquo;既圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7dyzt8ic\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7dyzt8ic&h=01943c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kmv23tyo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkmv23tyo&h=79e4e7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g9sxfr5l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg9sxfr5l&h=19c9f7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sa6xco8m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsa6xco8m&h=947c5d59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5ner60fd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5ner60fd&h=f78bf611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仰光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7tw0baci\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7tw0baci&h=5c27b0cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mtnbr7u0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmtnbr7u0&h=35fa60d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柏安 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9yczf54j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9yczf54j&h=49080fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gzt6d7b4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgzt6d7b4&h=78b24807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒲甘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dr10ws7g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdr10ws7g&h=4b590fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eyus8lfv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feyus8lfv&h=fb4edf8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i936x0eb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi936x0eb&h=0487fb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2fzxpmi1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2fzxpmi1&h=c6960125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茵萊湖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7ri4l026\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7ri4l026&h=b0810e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ipg1w5lq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fipg1w5lq&h=aa6ab553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏木橋"},{"pid":"04381f0522051d6097d8669fe92823a2f0131e80","tid":365753,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:08:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"312ef3aaf0cba955d3fb2691ab7526b5e77a3d93","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:40:40.000Z","msg":"先講少少緬甸背景, 細佬我其實都係一知半解, 但都試下拋下磚, 有錯請指正<br />\n相信大家都聽講昂山素姬呢個人, 而我都係透過聽過呢昂山素姬呢個名而認識緬甸. 緬甸係2010年開始開啟左所謂既改革開放, 慢慢開放國家, 令到其他人可以去緬甸. 從果時開始, 車都慢慢引入, 最後搞到仰光極多車, 塞車已經係仰光既其中一個&rdquo;特點&rdquo;. <br />\n開放左國家大約都係7年, 當然有好多人會想賺遊客錢, 呢個都無可口非, 但係整體黎講, 都未算好商業化, 仲保存到佢既特色. 我覺得我仲係能夠好感受到呢個國家,見識同欣賞到呢個緬甸. <br />\n我total 去左17-18日, 到最後果幾日甚至覺得開始悶, 想走. 但返左黎香港一排, 我覺得我遲2-3年會再返去緬甸望下<br />\n<br />\n而我今次既緬甸之旅都叫玩左大部份緬甸城市: 仰光, 帕安, 蒲甘, 茵萊湖, 曼德勒<br />\n每個地方都有佢既特色, 唔同既感受<br />\n<br />\n先講下我覺得緬甸有咩特別先, 例如佢地好輕著一種叫籠基(longyi) 既野包住, 男男女女都係咁, 而我就緊係有買返條扮下緬甸仔仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 再加上太陽好曬, 又無搽防曬, 曬得一面古銅色皮膚, 同緬甸人皮膚有幾分相似, 最後俾人誤以為我係緬甸人, 同我講緬甸話, 都唔知應唔應該開心好. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/212925_04e80af0131520959f2bc5d28a4f5a48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F212925_04e80af0131520959f2bc5d28a4f5a48.jpg&h=defdec8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地好鍾意搽天然既特納卡(Thanakha)<br />\n示意圖: <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/213415_bb0f124329d5d28598a7290fc556ff5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F213415_bb0f124329d5d28598a7290fc556ff5a.jpg&h=712c5644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三樣係佢地真係好鍾意著拖鞋, 幾乎每一個人都係著拖鞋, 我諗其中一個原因係佢地仲落後, 好多地方都係泥路, 著拖鞋而洗? 第二個原因係佢地入寺廟係要除鞋先入得, 所以著拖鞋係方便既<br />\n而我的確覺我著拖鞋係方便D, 所以即使我有波鞋, 我大部份時間都係著拖鞋, 隻腳曬左個拖鞋印出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖: 連見美帝都著住霸氣拖鞋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/213651_dc38ad42b68767f09bdc4b8f61014449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F213651_dc38ad42b68767f09bdc4b8f61014449.jpg&h=058d96d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27809eb451f346702f4bedf987781c0e8633540d","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古銅色圖呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黑到排得住緬甸仔仔膚色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4aff64c37ba601f38d0e7fd334188640bd26843","tid":365753,"uid":72531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c639f82ad28542ffedadb1fbe54b19a19081980","tid":365753,"uid":23560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"師兄你咁近影到啲漁夫嘅<br />\n上次去只可遠好遠咁睇<br />\n<br />\n不過緬甸真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3e0906243c6516ab8fd24c85383794921ba138","tid":365753,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:38:53.000Z","msg":"之前想去，但d交通好似好難搞，放棄咗"},{"pid":"6c11473f5ae271d4e540ea27fe2bf9ee62a95886","tid":365753,"uid":59066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"留名學野<br />\n<br />\n下年去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc84f65c58c316084fdc666caf350874329ad82","tid":365753,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"預計九月中至尾到緬甸<br />\n但仲搵緊點搞簽証 入唔入到都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a3458e302a07bacd08daf08fb9dd2220a5c54a","tid":365753,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:02:02.000Z","msg":"踢拖圖呢？"},{"pid":"3bbe95d5dd149c53f592c44aa77c0122126d6565","tid":365753,"uid":60173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:05:21.000Z","msg":"出快d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b16408acec71cdee0767b36a7813ec0bcc84dc","tid":365753,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T02:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預計九月中至尾到緬甸<br />\n但仲搵緊點搞簽証 入唔入到都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你可以去灣仔領事館搞，一係比USD$50搞e-visa"},{"pid":"81be02c7df7b7a330fa6a95426a3b7200763f16e","tid":365753,"uid":129765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"請問一共用了多小錢"},{"pid":"14adab744b836e2239200403b7068d86f3c6312d","tid":365753,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dac9baf5c62fa658fe46cfa4f56693d3371d747","tid":365753,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>預計九月中至尾到緬甸<br />\n但仲搵緊點搞簽証 入唔入到都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你可以去灣仔領事館搞，一係比USD$50搞e-visa</blockquote><br />\n我上網查過<br />\nEvisa 唔可以印度經陸路入 <br />\n仲煩惱緊<br />\n利申 單車環亞歐非 現已在尼泊爾 差唔多出發去印度"},{"pid":"077b03f2c94da6535b16b60d14ea8384d1ed04ad","tid":365753,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"點解d車得白色既?"},{"pid":"d7a876baa283eb3d502ded9084c1ddd65515ead5","tid":365753,"uid":9773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T07:00:48.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n岩岩5月去完返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想再去"},{"pid":"378fc77b7db52bcdcf3fa18c2ab1545584fb68f0","tid":365753,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"留名支持，茵萊湖近影漁夫張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年前去過，雖然唔太溝通到但係人極友善，景亦靚，印象中由頭到尾都無俾人呃過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過小心飲食，中過一次招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a943ad6d24f419317b60281a6e4c2748114203","tid":365753,"uid":26844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名支持，茵萊湖近影漁夫張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年前去過，雖然唔太溝通到但係人極友善，景亦靚，印象中由頭到尾都無俾人呃過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過小心飲食，中過一次招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可講多少少？<br />\n係食貴左 唔衛生 定唔好味？<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"ba2e2422b9baffdaf513569343bfdcd4693a72dc","tid":365753,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名支持，茵萊湖近影漁夫張相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾年前去過，雖然唔太溝通到但係人極友善，景亦靚，印象中由頭到尾都無俾人呃過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過小心飲食，中過一次招 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可講多少少？<br />\n係食貴左 唔衛生 定唔好味？<br />\nThanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸胃炎，可能係有餐早餐食既涼菜，亦可能係之前個晚食個辣蟹煲出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放心個度食野好平，亦大致衛生，記得係蒲甘遺跡，有堆攤檔，三四十港紙就有大餐食，白飯任裝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24d83eeeec30e72ba511fafc01331eb09906d23","tid":365753,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"有無條女資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同國家既靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eefb4692675d49b4cc62cdfedd2acb27247cb147","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄你咁近影到啲漁夫嘅<br />\n上次去只可遠好遠咁睇<br />\n<br />\n不過緬甸真係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地叫個船fu哥哥帶我地去搵漁夫<br />\n個漁夫好好人咁係咁擺pose 俾我地影, 最後當然有問我地拎tips, 但我地見佢咁熱心又無散紙係身, 都俾左唔少tips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926ab4027852a8a0ad82f4d97dbfc0f160920d04","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前想去，但d交通好似好難搞，放棄咗</blockquote><br />\n其實睇落真係幾複雜同埋人生路不熟, 唔敢行出第一步 (我自己都係咁)<br />\n但去到果度, 你肯問下人, 其他人/hostel staff會教你點搭車, 我都係每次去問hostel staff / 去附近果d 旅行店買車飛<br />\n<br />\n結論: 唔好怯, 你敢買機票, 之後既野就變得好輕鬆"},{"pid":"cefa27a38b060ae9b4652336d4ae9d7a576bbedc","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學野<br />\n<br />\n下年去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識野, 去完share 返"},{"pid":"be93237dd3ae2aab2e7119a7b7fa6e33d63937d1","tid":365753,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>預計九月中至尾到緬甸<br />\n但仲搵緊點搞簽証 入唔入到都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你可以去灣仔領事館搞，一係比USD$50搞e-visa</blockquote><br />\n我上網查過<br />\nEvisa 唔可以印度經陸路入 <br />\n仲煩惱緊<br />\n利申 單車環亞歐非 現已在尼泊爾 差唔多出發去印度</blockquote><br />\n巴打勁阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加油"}]}